description:
Thin Lizzy - Paradise By The Soundboard (Deluxe 2-CD)1978 ak320

Thin Lizzy are a hard rock band formed in Dublin, Ireland in 1969. Their music reflects a wide range of influences, including blues, soul music, psychedelic rock, and traditional Irish folk music, but is generally classified as hard rock or sometimes heavy metal. Rolling Stone magazine describes the band as distinctly hard rock, "far apart from the braying mid-70s metal pack"In 1978 they played at the Paradise Theater in Boston MA. It was a great show 
So here it is...

Scott Gorham – guitar, backing vocals (1974–83, 1996–2001, 2004–present)
